name: Sunset Mercury 1975-2011. V2
description: The North American car brand Mercury, belonging to the Ford Motor Company, disappeared from the automotive market in 2010. But its history is well worth remembering. Postcard that I offered for free some time ago however when H = N made the contract change the postcardsNFTs were registered with an error. I apologize to 8 collectors who obtained one of them. For this reason I am going to give away 100 again. I sincerely hope that the platform does not have to "burn" the NFts again with another contract update. Greetings Gustavo.
